<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٣- عبد الله بن مَسْلَمة القَعْنَبِي.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٤- محمدُ بن خالد بن عَثْمَةَ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
